We recently got married here inside Mandalay Bay at the House of Blues (at the Crossroads Restaurant).
It was a unique venue that allowed us to personalize our wedding and add extra details that made it unique and special to us and our guests.
There is a stage on one end of the space and a bar on the other.
We performed a few songs on the stage and our guests enjoyed the open bar, southern-style food and groovy atmosphere.
The wedding coordinator for the HOB, Amber, was a dream to work with.
She and she staff were very professional and they helped make our Big Day stress-free.
Our guests said it was one of the most unforgettable weddings that they have ever been to and we have Amber and the HOB staff to thank for that.

